{"tid":563613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FB有殺錯無放過","createTime":"2018-02-17T06:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T06:52:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b88e7e3c398898d8a85b8514a2b4649928200183","tid":563613,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:09:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20180216/20306707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180216%2F20306707&d=825nkqZtgwYwYKRIcmS6Ap4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b7119c14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180216%2F20306707&h=8f6a0bc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20180216/20306707</a><br />\n<br />\nFB有殺錯無放過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n20,574<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180216/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180216%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=5f07ea7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高慧然fb截圖<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nFB無數次封鎖我、禁止我發表言論。短則三天、長則一個月，已反覆數次。這一次，大約是永久禁止我使用此平台了，以莫須有的理由。<br />\n<br />\n曾幾何時，由美國人創辦的社交平台FB被想當然地認為必然符合美國精神：崇尚自由、尊重個人言論自由。但是，自從由中國人陳澍管理台灣及香港FB事務後，FB採用檢舉制度，但凡有人檢舉，FB一定有殺錯無放過。我曾經因為轉發一篇報章文章而被檢舉、刪文，並接到警告。而我只是轉發文章，沒有發表任何言論。也有網友轉發澳門觀光塔笨豬跳新聞而被刪文、警告。無他的，只要接到檢舉，不管有理無理，FB都會先行刪文。這是把中國網絡管制的手法搬到了台灣與香港。<br />\n<br />\n最荒謬的是，FB常常用舊文來封鎖我的言論。FB守則新舊標準大不同，舊時允許的言論，今日不被允許了，結果FB用新守則去監管舊post，一旦發現舊post的言論不符新守則，便馬上封鎖我。有一次，有人找到一篇舊post檢舉我，FB「移除基於種族、民族、國籍、宗教、性傾向、性別或肢體殘障攻擊他人的帖子」，並且封鎖我。而我只是寫了一句話：「天譴是有理由的。」，並無針對任何人。<br />\n<br />\n當FB變成微博，限制使用者的言論。離棄FB成為大勢所趨，它不用封鎖我，我遲早會尋找更適合的平台。大家若有介紹，請告訴我。暫時，這個後備FB仍可使用：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyoko&d=825nkqZtgwYwYKRIcmS6Ap4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=61307feb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko</a>  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk <br />\n網頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyoko&d=825nkqZtgwYwYKRIcmS6Ap4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=61307feb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n才剛剛開始 (蔣芸)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n左、右的問題 (古德明)"},{"pid":"ca9b2c2895b602b8360e2f0512a1ecc2b3facd38","tid":563613,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:50:06.000Z","msg":"全世界都奶共，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e52c18bcb5c98f585be95524192435087f12a19","tid":563613,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:52:34.000Z","msg":"極端到on99<br />\n雖然fb真係好多假新聞賣假野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多到令人髮指<br />\n<br />\n今次咁搞都唔知係好事定壞事"}]}